{"title":"Orto Odontogeriatria-2026","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Ortogeriatría/Orto Odontogeriatria-2026.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"ODONTOGERIATRÍA","guid":"BdZQW9mhU0SxI_tXfYzgrA","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Definición y Fundamentos","guid":"Mk2RjueqJ0GgZiTv7AXF9g","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"Rama de odontología con base\\Nen conocimientos **geriátricos\\Ny gerontológicos**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"Atención adaptada a condiciones\\Nespecíficas de la **persona mayor**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"Pilar fundamental → **atención\\Ncentrada en el usuario**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"1","text":"Modelo INGER (Dra. Javiera\\NEspinoza) → **único en Chile**","guid":"","children":[{"id":"6","parent":"5","text":"Integración interdisciplinaria dentro\\Nde unidades geriátricas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"7","parent":"5","text":"Atención flexible → box dental,\\Ncama, silla de ruedas, domicilio","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"8","parent":"1","text":"OMS declara → **\"Salud oral es\\Nárea crucial y descuidada del\\Nenvejecimiento saludable\"**","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"9","parent":"0","text":"Anatomía y Fisiología Oral\\Nen el Envejecimiento","guid":"kspl1K0-l0uVJXK-V5u3Hg","children":[{"id":"10","parent":"9","text":"Dentadura permanente","guid":"","children":[{"id":"11","parent":"10","text":"32 dientes en 4 cuadrantes\\N(nomenclatura FDI)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"12","parent":"10","text":"Cuadrante 1 → superior\\Nderecho, sentido horario","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"13","parent":"9","text":"Cambios del esmalte","guid":"","children":[{"id":"14","parent":"13","text":"Tejido más duro del cuerpo\\N→ **hidroxiapatita**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"15","parent":"13","text":"**pH crítico 5.5** →\\Ndesmineralización","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"13","text":"Envejecimiento → desgaste, traslucidez →\\N**dientes amarillos es normal**","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"17","parent":"9","text":"Cambios de la dentina","guid":"","children":[{"id":"18","parent":"17","text":"**pH crítico 6.5** → más\\Nsusceptible que esmalte","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"17","text":"Aposición de **dentina terciaria**\\N→ reduce cámara pulpar","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"17","text":"Dentina\\Nesclerótica/reparativa\\Nfrente a noxas","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"21","parent":"9","text":"Complejo pulpo-dentinario","guid":"","children":[{"id":"22","parent":"21","text":"Fibras C → dolor sordo,\\Ncrónico (única sensación)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"21","text":"**Pulpitis** → dolor intenso por\\Nausencia de espacio expansión","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"24","parent":"9","text":"Periodonto","guid":"","children":[{"id":"25","parent":"24","text":"Si diente se pierde → **hueso\\Nalveolar se reabsorbe**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"26","parent":"24","text":"Sarro → biofilm calcificado →\\Ngingivitis → periodontitis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"27","parent":"24","text":"Metaloproteinasas →\\Ndestrucción ósea progresiva","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"28","parent":"9","text":"Cavidad Oral (Anatomía quirúrgica)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"29","parent":"28","text":"Labio, encía, dientes,\\Npaladar duro/blando","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"28","text":"Lengua (2/3 anteriores), piso de boca","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"28","text":"Mucosa bucal, trígono retromolar","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"32","parent":"0","text":"Epidemiología Global de Salud\\NOral en Adultos Mayores","guid":"ON-h1udq9E2kSC50BGtNOg","children":[{"id":"33","parent":"32","text":"Datos Chile (ENS)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"34","parent":"33","text":"**Desdentados totales 30%**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"33","text":"**Desdentados parciales 69.8%**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"33","text":"Solo 37.1% usa prótesis\\Nen ambos maxilares","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"37","parent":"32","text":"Datos Internacionales (ECG/EUGMS)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"38","parent":"37","text":"Pérdida de dientes en países altos\\Ningresos → hasta **35%**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"37","text":"Hasta **67%** usuarios prótesis →\\Ncondiciones relacionadas con ellas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"37","text":"Estudio NY (AM confinados en hogar)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"41","parent":"40","text":"78.9% con dientes →\\Nal menos 1 caries","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"40","text":"45.6% necesitaba extracciones","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"40","text":"25.8% con prótesis en mal estado","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"44","parent":"37","text":"Hiposalivación/xerostomía\\N→ **30%** ≥65 años","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"45","parent":"0","text":"Impacto\\NMultidimensional de la\\NSalud Oral","guid":"V4sVXlEuP0mg8D8a_Fgfyw","children":[{"id":"46","parent":"45","text":"Esfera social y emocional","guid":"","children":[{"id":"47","parent":"46","text":"Pérdida dental → taparse al reír,\\Nevitar comer con otros","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"46","text":"Alteración autopercepción → **duelo** →\\Nenvejecimiento prematuro percibido","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"46","text":"Impacto **independiente\\Ndel estado cognitivo**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"50","parent":"46","text":"Halitosis → daña\\Nbienestar psicosocial","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"51","parent":"45","text":"Esfera cognitiva","guid":"","children":[{"id":"52","parent":"51","text":"Función masticatoria → estímulo\\Nperiférico → **activa neocórtex**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"51","text":"Pérdida dentaria → ↑ riesgo\\N**deterioro cognitivo y demencia**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"54","parent":"51","text":"Estudio Ohasama → periodontitis severa +\\Nmás dientes = ↑ atrofia hipocampal","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"55","parent":"45","text":"Esfera funcional","guid":"","children":[{"id":"56","parent":"55","text":"Pérdida dental → colapso facial →\\Nalteración masticación/deglución/habla","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"57","parent":"55","text":"Déficit nutricional secundario","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"55","text":"**Examen oral + prueba masticatoria →\\Nparte de ingreso geriátrico**","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"59","parent":"45","text":"Impacto en Paliativos","guid":"","children":[{"id":"60","parent":"59","text":"Boca = fuente de confort y\\Nplacer (comer, hablar, besar)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"61","parent":"59","text":"Pero también de **gran sufrimiento**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"59","text":"Impacto funcional →\\Ntragar, hablar, comer","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"59","text":"Impacto social → vergüenza, aislamiento,\\N\"más paciente que persona\"","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"64","parent":"0","text":"Fragilidad Oral → **Nuevo\\NSíndrome Geriátrico**","guid":"PPppUE3H0ES5wkKiwNWyaQ","children":[{"id":"65","parent":"64","text":"Definición (Estudio Kashiwa, Japón)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"66","parent":"65","text":"Estado deficiente en **≥3\\Nindicadores** orales","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"67","parent":"64","text":"Indicadores de fragilidad oral","guid":"","children":[{"id":"68","parent":"67","text":"Número de dientes remanentes","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"67","text":"Enfermedad periodontal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"67","text":"Dificultad masticatoria","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"67","text":"Dificultad deglutoria (disfagia)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"67","text":"Xerostomía","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"73","parent":"67","text":"Fuerza de mordida disminuida","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"67","text":"Presión de lengua disminuida","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"67","text":"Habilidad motora oral articulatoria","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"76","parent":"64","text":"Asociaciones (revisión\\Nsistemática Dibello 2025)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"77","parent":"76","text":"4 indicadores → deterioro cognitivo, DCL,\\Ndemencia, depresión tardía","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"76","text":"Deterioro salud oral + disfagia →\\Nmayor asociación con outcomes","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"79","parent":"76","text":"Dolor oral → asociado\\N**solo** a depresión tardía","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"80","parent":"64","text":"Outcomes predichos","guid":"","children":[{"id":"81","parent":"80","text":"**Fragilidad física**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"80","text":"**Sarcopenia**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"80","text":"**Necesidad de\\Ncuidados a largo\\Nplazo**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"84","parent":"80","text":"**Mortalidad**","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"85","parent":"0","text":"Riesgo de Deterioro Rápido\\Nde Salud Oral (ROHD)","guid":"VkpU9o1UekOupbxhVIEhNQ","children":[{"id":"86","parent":"85","text":"Factores de riesgo → **Las 7-Ds**","guid":"","children":[{"id":"87","parent":"86","text":"**D**emencia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"86","text":"**D**epresión","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"89","parent":"86","text":"**D**estreza (Dexterity) →\\NParkinson, artritis reumatoide","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"90","parent":"86","text":"**D**rogas (Fármacos) → xerostomía","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"91","parent":"86","text":"**D**iabetes","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"92","parent":"86","text":"**D**esmotivación","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"86","text":"**D**ieta","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"94","parent":"85","text":"Consecuencias de boca\\Nseca y mal cuidado","guid":"","children":[{"id":"95","parent":"94","text":"Dificultad comer/tragar →\\Ndisfagi