t":"Periodontitis crónica → bacteriemias","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"114","parent":"100","text":"Enfermedad pulmonar","guid":"","children":[{"id":"115","parent":"114","text":"Cavidad oral = **reservorio de\\Npatógenos respiratorios**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"116","parent":"114","text":"Aspiración de bacterias orales →\\N**neumonía aspirativa**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"117","parent":"114","text":"Exacerbaciones de EPOC","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"118","parent":"114","text":"Mejor higiene oral → **previene ~1 de\\Ncada 10 muertes por neumonía** en\\Nhogares de ancianos","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"119","parent":"100","text":"Endocarditis infecciosa","guid":"","children":[{"id":"120","parent":"119","text":"**Factor de riesgo fuerte**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"121","parent":"119","text":"Cepillado en boca\\Ninflamada → bacteriemia","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"122","parent":"100","text":"Otras asociaciones","guid":"","children":[{"id":"123","parent":"122","text":"ERC → factor de riesgo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"124","parent":"122","text":"Artritis reumatoide → a clarificar","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"125","parent":"122","text":"Cáncer → a clarificar","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"126","parent":"0","text":"Evaluación de Salud Oral\\Npor el Médico/Geriatra","guid":"eLyy3S4Xa0ea4v_MjKWU4g","children":[{"id":"127","parent":"126","text":"6 Preguntas Clave (ECG/EUGMS)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"128","parent":"127","text":"1. ¿Hay algo que le moleste en la\\Nboca? → SÍ: examen + derivar","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"129","parent":"127","text":"2. ¿Siente la boca seca? → SÍ:\\Nrevisar fármacos, intervenir","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"130","parent":"127","text":"3. ¿Tiene dientes naturales, prótesis o\\Nambos? → guía siguientes","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"131","parent":"127","text":"4. ¿Con qué frecuencia se cepilla? →\\N<1x/día: aconsejar, examinar","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"132","parent":"127","text":"5. ¿Le sangran las encías? →\\NSÍ: examen + derivar","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"133","parent":"127","text":"6. ¿Visita al dentista en últimos 12\\Nmeses? → NO: examen + derivar","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"134","parent":"126","text":"OHAT (Oral Health Assessment Tool)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"135","parent":"134","text":"8 categorías: labios, lengua, encías, saliva,\\Ndientes, prótesis, limpieza, dolor","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"136","parent":"134","text":"Puntuación 0-2\\N(saludable/cambios/no\\Nsaludable)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"137","parent":"134","text":"Puntuación alta → derivación dental","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"138","parent":"126","text":"ROAG (Revised Oral\\NAssessment Guide)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"139","parent":"138","text":"Para pacientes paliativos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"140","parent":"138","text":"Evalúa labios, mucosas, lengua,\\Nencías, dientes/prótesis, saliva","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"141","parent":"138","text":"Puntuación 1-3 (normal/severo)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"142","parent":"138","text":"Grados 2-3 → necesitan intervención","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"143","parent":"126","text":"Signos de Alerta para\\NDerivación URGENTE","guid":"","children":[{"id":"144","parent":"143","text":"Caries → manchas\\Nmarrones/negras, cavidades","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"145","parent":"143","text":"Periodontitis → encías rojas,\\Nhinchadas, sangrado","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"146","parent":"143","text":"**Cáncer oral** → cualquier lesión\\N**>2 semanas** sin sanar","guid":"","children":[{"id":"147","parent":"146","text":"Úlceras, placas\\Nblancas/rojas que no\\Ncuran","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"148","parent":"146","text":"Cambio color/forma/volumen mucosa","guid":"","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"149","parent":"0","text":"Xerostomía (Boca Seca)","guid":"2jp-YfG1JUOKP27kJM_xew","children":[{"id":"150","parent":"149","text":"Etiología farmacológica","guid":"","childre