rio (5 gotas)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"174","parent":"171","text":"**Bajo costo y efectiva**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"175","parent":"171","text":"Sustitutos salivales\\Ncomerciales (geles, sprays)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"176","parent":"171","text":"Sorbos frecuentes de agua","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"177","parent":"171","text":"Chicles sin azúcar con xilitol","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"178","parent":"171","text":"Lubricantes labiales (evitar\\Nbase petróleo con O2)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"179","parent":"171","text":"Sialogogos (pilocarpina, cevimelina)\\Nsi glándulas funcionales","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"180","parent":"0","text":"Prótesis Dentales","guid":"oTi7Mox1PEKMsSJ46e7C9w","children":[{"id":"181","parent":"180","text":"Características","guid":"","children":[{"id":"182","parent":"181","text":"Material acrílico → **poroso** →\\Nacumula bacterias/hongos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"183","parent":"181","text":"Vida útil recomendada → **<5 años**","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"184","parent":"180","text":"Cuidados obligatorios","guid":"","children":[{"id":"185","parent":"184","text":"**RETIRAR SIEMPRE\\NPARA DORMIR**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"186","parent":"184","text":"Limpieza con cepillo + jabón\\Nneutro (NO pasta dental)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"187","parent":"184","text":"Pastillas efervescentes →\\Ncomplemento, no reemplazo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"188","parent":"184","text":"**Etiquetar prótesis** en instituciones","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"189","parent":"180","text":"Nuevo protocolo","guid":"","children":[{"id":"190","parent":"189","text":"**Mantener en SECO durante\\Nla noche** (no en agua)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"191","parent":"189","text":"Humedecer antes de usar","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"192","parent":"189","text":"↓ Proliferación bacteriana/fúngica","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"193","parent":"180","text":"Complicaciones","guid":"","children":[{"id":"194","parent":"193","text":"**Estomatitis subprotésica** →\\Neritema en paladar, candidiasis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"195","parent":"193","text":"Hiperplasia tisular por\\Nirritación crónica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"196","parent":"193","text":"Úlceras traumáticas, mal ajuste","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"197","parent":"0","text":"Terapias de Remineralización","guid":"3zMcr7rxc0iFCDGgVhZrYw","children":[{"id":"198","parent":"197","text":"Pasta dental","guid":"","children":[{"id":"199","parent":"198","text":"**Alta concentración\\Nflúor 5.000 ppm**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"200","parent":"198","text":"**NO SE ENJUAGA** →\\Nescupir exceso, dejar actuar","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"201","parent":"197","text":"Post-aplicación flúor profesional","guid":"","children":[{"id":"202","parent":"201","text":"No tomar líquidos por 1 hora","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"203","parent":"201","text":"No comer por 1 hora","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"204","parent":"201","text":"No lavar dientes hasta día siguiente","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"205","parent":"197","text":"Barnices de flúor","guid":"","children":[{"id":"206","parent":"205","text":"22.600 ppm (aplicación profesional)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"207","parent":"205","text":"Clorhexidina o **fluoruro de\\Ndiamino de plata (SDF)** →\\Ndetiene caries radiculares","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"208","parent":"197","text":"Objetivo","guid":"","children":[{"id":"209","parent":"208","text":"Detener avance de caries","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"210","parent":"208","text":"Fortalecer estructura dental","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"211","parent":"0","text":"Candidiasis Oral","guid":"LFgiZtXWj0K2M7NmIO9zpQ","children":[{"id":"212","parent":"211","text":"Presentaciones","guid":"","children":[{"id":"213","parent":"212","text":"**Pseudomembranosa** →\\Nplacas blancas raspables","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"214","parent":"212","text":"**Eritematosa** →\\Nenrojecimiento sin placas","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"215","parent":"211","text":"Factores predisponentes","guid":"","children":[{"id":"216","parent":"215","text":"Hiposalivación","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"217","parent":"215","text":"Mala higiene oral/protésica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"218","parent":"215","text":"Diabetes","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"219","parent":"215","text":"Inmunosupresión","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"220","parent":"215","text":"Fármacos (corticoides, ATB)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"221","parent":"211","text":"Tratamiento","guid":"","children":[{"id":"222","parent":"221","text":"**Fluconazol 150 mg dosis\\Núnica** → altamente efectivo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"223","parent":"221","text":"Nistatina tópica →\\Nrequiere mayor adherencia","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"224","parent":"0","text":"Mucositis Oral","guid":"YAgudwAhQke2wJkgTRoQRg","children":[{"id":"225","parent":"224","text":"Definición → inflamación\\Ndolorosa de mucosa oral","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"226","parent":"224","text":"Incidencia → **~80%**\\Npacientes oncológicos (QT/RT)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"227","parent":"224","text":"Manejo","guid":"","children":[{"id":"228","parent":"227","text":"**Spray oral de Indometacina** →\\Nalivia dolor en ~25 min","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"229","parent":"227","text":"Analgésicos sistémicos\\Nsegún escala OMS","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"230","parent":"227","text":"Higiene oral suave","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"231","parent":"227","text":"Evitar irritantes","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"232","parent":"0","text":"Antirresortivos y MRONJ","guid":"qBsmR62xKUeQfwZBYVI7EA","children":[{"id":"233","parent":"232","text":"Riesgo bajo pero\\Ncomplicación severa","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"234","parent":"232","text":"**Pase dental\\Npre-tratamiento\\NFUNDAMENTAL**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"235","parent":"232","text":"Identificar y eliminar focos infección\\NANTES de iniciar terapia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"236","parent":"232","text":"Dientes mal pronóstico, periodontitis\\Nsevera → resolver primero","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"237","parent":"0","text":"Profilaxis Antibiótica","guid":"wHSw4yCaRketgiIN1pWkzg","children":[{"id":"238","parent":"237","text":"Indicaciones absolutas para\\Nprocedimientos invasivos","guid":"","children":[{"id":"239","parent":"238","text":"Válvulas cardíacas protésicas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"240","parent":"238","text":"Historia de endocarditis infecciosa","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"241","parent":"238","text":"Cardiopatías congénitas no\\Nreparadas/defectos residuales","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"242","parent":"237","text":"Paciente\\Nfrágil/múltiples\\Ncomorbilidades","guid":"","children":[{"id":"243","parent":"242","text":"**No indicación absoluta**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"244","parent":"242","text":"Decisión consensuada\\Ncon equipo médico","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"245","parent":"0","text":"Hiperplasia Gingival Farmacológica","guid":"h5j_kGL35UqztlBsPrrTLA","children":[{"id":"246","parent":"245","text":"Bloqueadores de canales de calcio","guid":"","children":[{"id":"247","parent":"246","text":"**Nifedipino**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"248","parent":"246","text":"**Diltiazem**","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"249","parent":"245","text":"Manifestación","guid":"","children":[{"id":"250","parent":"249","text":"Crecimiento gingival progresivo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"251","parent":"249","text":"Dificulta higiene →\\Nempeora periodontitis","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"252","parent":"0","text":"Cáncer de Cavidad Oral","guid":"QSZIdH4tY0u6Fiizgvyxrw","children":[{"id":"253","parent":"252","text":"Epidemiología","guid":"","children":[{"id":"254","parent":"253","text":"**6ª causa de cáncer en el mundo**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"255","parent":"253","text":"200.000 casos/año, 100.000 muertes","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"256","parent":"253","text":"Más frecuente en hombres","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"257","parent":"253","text":"Histología más común →\\N**carcinoma células escamosas**","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"258","parent":"252","text":"Factores de Riesgo","guid":"","children":[{"id":"259","parent":"258","text":"**Tabaco** → 12-15 veces","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"260","parent":"258","text":"**Alcohol** → 6 veces","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"261","parent":"258","text":"Tabaco + Alcohol →\\N**15 veces más**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"262","parent":"258","text":"VPH 16 → 5 veces","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"263","parent":"258","text":"Inmunosupresión (VIH,\\Ntrasplantados) → 2-4 veces","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"264","parent":"258","text":"Enfermedad periodontal crónica","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"265","parent":"252","text":"Sitios y Pronóstico","guid":"","children":[{"id":"266","parent":"265","text":"**Lengua** → sitio más común, **peor\\Npronóstico** (sobrevida 5 años 27-39%)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"267","parent":"265","text":"Piso de boca → alta tasa invasión\\Nmandibular y metástasis ganglionar","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"268","parent":"265","text":"Labio → 25%,\\Ngeneralmente etapas\\Ntempranas","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"269","parent":"252","text":"Signos de Alarma →\\NDERIVAR URGENTE","guid":"","children":[{"id":"270","parent":"269","text":"Úlcera o lesión que **NO\\Nsana en 2 semanas**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"271","parent":"269","text":"Placa blanca/roja persistente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"272","parent":"269","text":"Cambio de color, forma o\\Nvolumen en mucosa","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"273","parent":"252","text":"Cirugía Comando","guid":"","children":[{"id":"274","parent":"273","text":"**COM**bined **MA**ndibulectomy and\\N**N**eck **D**issection **O**peration","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"275","parent":"273","text":"Para estadio III y IVa/b","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"276","parent":"273","text":"Resección en bloque:\\Nhemiglosectomía +\\Nhemimandibulectomía + disección\\Nradical cuello","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"277","parent":"0","text":"Cuidado Oral en\\NPaliativos/Final de Vida","guid":"mGgqncCCfkC9qil3SMvlFg","children":[{"id":"278","parent":"277","text":"Pilares del cuidado","guid":"","children":[{"id":"279","parent":"278","text":"Mantener higiene, humedad y confort","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"280","parent":"278","text":"Frecuencia > tipo de producto","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"281","parent":"278","text":"Lubricación mucosa cada 1-2\\Nhoras en xerostomía severa","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"282","parent":"277","text":"Procedimiento básico","guid":"","children":[{"id":"283","parent":"282","text":"1. Evaluación sistemática (ROAG)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"284","parent":"282","text":"2. Lubricación labios →\\Nvaselina o cremas base agua","guid":"","children":[{"id":"285","parent":"284","text":"**Evitar bálsamos base petróleo**\\N(riesgo inflamabilidad con O2)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"286","parent":"282","text":"3. Limpieza dientes/mucosas","guid":"","children":[{"id":"287","parent":"286","text":"Cepillo suave, cabezal pequeño","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"288","parent":"286","text":"Pasta **sin Lauril Sulfato de Sodio\\N(LSS)** → irrita mucosa seca","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"289","parent":"286","text":"Mucosas → gasa + suero fisiológico","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"290","parent":"282","text":"4. Lubricación mucosas →\\Nsustitutos salivales","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"291","parent":"277","text":"Glicerina → usar con precaución","guid":"","children":[{"id":"292","parent":"291","text":"Pura (85%) es\\N**deshidratante** →\\NEVITAR","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"293","parent":"291","text":"Si se usa → diluir a **17%**\\N(10 mL en 40 mL agua)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"294","parent":"291","text":"Alivio inmediato pero corta duración","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"295","parent":"277","text":"Final de vida","guid":"","children":[{"id":"296","parent":"295","text":"Prioridad absoluta →\\N**humectación regular de\\Nmucosas**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"297","parent":"295","text":"Objetivo exclusivo → **CONFORT**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"298","parent":"295","text":"Hisopos de espuma o\\Ngasas con agua/suero","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"299","parent":"295","text":"**Retirar prótesis** en\\Ninconscientes → riesgo\\Naspiración","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"300","parent":"0","text":"Modelo Interdisciplinario UGA-INGER","guid":"fU4bhAs3MEeR0UjMqEw_qA","children":[{"id":"301","parent":"300","text":"Pilares","guid":"","children":[{"id":"302","parent":"301","text":"Trabajo interdisciplinario","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"303","parent":"301","text":"Atención centrada en la persona","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"304","parent":"301","text":"Restablecimiento funcionalidad oral","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"305","parent":"301","text":"Odontología de mínima intervención","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"306","parent":"300","text":"Interacciones clave","guid":"","children":[{"id":"307","parent":"306","text":"Enfermería → higiene oral\\Ndiaria (**aseo menor**)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"308","parent":"306","text":"Fonoaudiología → consistencias,\\Ndeglución, adaptación protésica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"309","parent":"306","text":"Terapia ocupacional → adaptar\\Nelementos higiene oral","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"310","parent":"306","text":"Kinesiología → transferencia segura","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"311","parent":"306","text":"Nutrición → dieta según\\Ncapacidad masticatoria","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"312","parent":"306","text":"Farmacia clínica →\\Npolifarmacia y efectos orales","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"313","parent":"300","text":"Priorización derivaciones INGER","guid":"","children":[{"id":"314","parent":"313","text":"1º Reparación prótesis (función\\Nmasticatoria/deglutoria)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"315","parent":"313","text":"2º Pases dentales\\Npara antirresortivos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"316","parent":"313","text":"3º Tratamiento no urgente\\Nmejora funcionalidad","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"317","parent":"313","text":"4º Evaluación ingresos nuevos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"318","parent":"313","text":"**Urgencias\\N(dolor/infección) →\\Ntransversales**","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"319","parent":"0","text":"Consejería en Salud\\NOral (ECG/EUGMS)","guid":"TYoi-D6Gk0ef-JYMF0R2bQ","children":[{"id":"320","parent":"319","text":"Cuidado diario de dientes","guid":"","children":[{"id":"321","parent":"320","text":"Cepillar **2 veces/día por 2\\Nminutos** con pasta fluorada","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"322","parent":"320","text":"Cepillo suave, adaptar si\\Nproblemas destreza","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"323","parent":"320","text":"Limpiar espacios interdentales\\N(cepillos interdentales, irrigadores)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"324","parent":"320","text":"Limpiar lengua diariamente","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"325","parent":"319","text":"Cuidado diario de prótesis","guid":"","children":[{"id":"326","parent":"325","text":"Cepillar 2x/día con cepillo\\Nespecial + jabón líquido","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"327","parent":"325","text":"**NO usar pasta dental** (abrasiva)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"328","parent":"325","text":"Combinar limpieza mecánica\\N+ química (tabletas)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"329","parent":"325","text":"**Retirar por la noche**","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"330","parent":"319","text":"Consejería dietética","guid":"","children":[{"id":"331","parent":"330","text":"Limitar azúcares y\\Nsnacks cariogénicos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"332","parent":"330","text":"Enjuagar boca con agua\\Ntras alimentos ácidos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"333","parent":"330","text":"Preferir medicamentos sin azúcar","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"334","parent":"319","text":"Revisiones dentales","guid":"","children":[{"id":"335","parent":"334","text":"**Cada 3-6 meses** si tiene dientes","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"336","parent":"334","text":"**Cada 12 meses** si edéntulo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"337","parent":"334","text":"Informar sobre atención domiciliaria","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"338","parent":"0","text":"Barreras para Salud Oral en\\NAM (ECG/EUGMS)","guid":"BtdtPV0XCk6vB8c_AXgboQ","children":[{"id":"339","parent":"338","text":"Relacionadas con la persona","guid":"","children":[{"id":"340","parent":"339","text":"Movilidad limitada, deterioro cognitivo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"341","parent":"339","text":"Bajo nivel educativo,\\Npoco conocimiento","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"342","parent":"339","text":"Desafíos financieros","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"343","parent":"339","text":"Miedo dental, actitudes negativas","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"344","parent":"338","text":"Falta de apoyo profesional","guid":"","children":[{"id":"345","parent":"344","text":"Formación limitada en gerodontología","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"346","parent":"344","text":"Poco conocimiento de\\Nno-dentales sobre salud oral","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"347","parent":"344","text":"Limitaciones\\Ntiempo/personal en\\Ninstituciones","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"348","parent":"338","text":"Falta de políticas efectivas","guid":"","children":[{"id":"349","parent":"348","text":"Salud oral no es prioridad","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"350","parent":"348","text":"Cobertura pública limitada","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"351","parent":"348","text":"Falta atención dental domiciliaria","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"352","parent":"0","text":"Perlas Clínicas ⭐","guid":"_M1gDV2fi0eOckLSxZFRww","children":[{"id":"353","parent":"352","text":"Dientes amarillos en AM es **NORMAL**\\N(desgaste esmalte → dentina visible)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"354","parent":"352","text":"pH crítico dentina (6.5) < esmalte (5.5) →\\N**raíces expuestas muy vulnerables**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"355","parent":"352","text":"Tratamiento periodontal = **intervención\\Nanti-diabética** (↓ HbA1c 0.4%)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"356","parent":"352","text":"Prótesis nocturnas → ↑ riesgo neumonía\\Naspirativa, **NO USAR DE NOCHE**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"357","parent":"352","text":"Prótesis guardar **EN SECO**\\Ndurante la noche (no en agua)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"358","parent":"352","text":"Pasta 5.000 ppm flúor → **NO\\NENJUAGAR**, escupir y dejar actuar","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"359","parent":"352","text":"Pase dental **ANTES** de\\Nantirresortivos → prevención MRONJ","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"360","parent":"352","text":"Saliva artificial casera (linaza) →\\Nsolución efectiva y económica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"361","parent":"352","text":"Fragilidad oral es predictor de fragilidad\\Nsistémica → **evaluar siempre**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"362","parent":"352","text":"Pérdida dentaria + periodontitis severa → ↑\\Natrofia hipocampal (Ohasama)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"363","parent":"352","text":"Higiene oral diaria por enfermería →\\Nparte del **aseo menor**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"364","parent":"352","text":"Mejor higiene oral → **previene\\N1/10 muertes por neumonía** en\\Nhogares ancianos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"365","parent":"352","text":"**Lesión oral >2 semanas** que\\Nno sana → derivar URGENTE\\N(descartar cáncer)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"366","parent":"352","text":"Glicerina pura (85%) es\\N**deshidratante** → usar diluida al\\N17%","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"367","parent":"352","text":"Cáncer lengua → **peor pronóstico**\\N(27-39% sobrevida 5 años)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"368","parent":"352","text":"Pasta sin **LSS** (Lauril Sulfato de Sodio)\\Nen mucosa sensible/paliativo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"369","parent":"352","text":"6 preguntas clave ECG/EUGMS →\\Ntamizaje rápido en consulta geriátrica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"370","parent":"352","text":"Las **7-Ds** → factores riesgo\\Ndeterioro rápido salud oral","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"371","parent":"0","text":"Referencias","guid":"","children":[{"id":"372","parent":"371","text":"1. Dibello V, et al. Targeting oral frailty indicators of late-life\\Ncognitive disorders and depression. Age Ageing. 2025;\\N54(7). DOI: 10.1093/ageing/afaf182","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"373","parent":"371","text":"2. Dibello V, et al. Oral frailty indicators and\\Ncardio- and cerebrovascular diseases in older\\Nage. Mech Ageing Dev. 2024;223:112010. DOI:\\N10.1016/j.mad.2024.112010","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"374","parent":"371","text":"3. Yamaguchi S, et al. Associations of Dental Health\\NWith the Progression of Hippocampal Atrophy.\\NNeurology. 2023;101(10):e1056-e1068. DOI: 10.\\N1212/WNL.0000000000207579","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"375","parent":"371","text":"4. Angst L, et al. Oral health and nutritional status in\\Ncare-dependent older adults. Swiss Dent J. 2024;134(2):\\N122-144. DOI: 10.61872/sdj-2024-02-09","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"376","parent":"371","text":"5. Espinoza González J. Guía de\\NOdontogeriatría y Salud Sistémica.\\NMaterial docente INGER. 2025.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"377","parent":"371","text":"6. De Visschere L, et al. European College of\\NGerodontology (ECG) & EUGMS. Policy\\NRecommendations on Oral Health. 2023.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"378","parent":"371","text":"7. Hoben M, et al. ECG/EUGMS Practical\\NGuide for Physicians on Oral Health Promotion\\Nin Frail Older Adults. 2023.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"379","parent":"371","text":"8. Kvalheim SF, Strand GV. Oral Care in\\NPalliative Patients. Int J Environ Res Public\\NHealth. 2022;19(10):6306.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"380","parent":"371","text":"9. Venkatasalu MR, et al. Oral health problems\\Namong palliative and terminally ill patients. BMC\\NOral Health. 2020;20:79.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"381","parent":"371","text":"10. Honold F, Correa F. Cirugía Comando\\N- Cáncer de Cavidad Oral. U\\NChile/Hospital del Salvador. 2019.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"382","parent":"371","text":"11. Salech F, et al. Epidemiología del uso de\\Nmedicamentos en el adulto mayor. Rev Med Clin\\NCondes. 2016;27(5):660-670.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":382,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"General","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Ortogeriatría","filename":"Orto Odontogeriatria-2026","id":"map_1537","resolved_references":[]}